div.h1: TSS Structure and ESP0 for Ring Transitions

div.p: Triggered by: INT instruction (syscall) Hardware interrupt CPU exception
If ESP0 is wrong corrupted stack crash!
Legend: Gold fields (esp0, ss0) are CRITICAL for ring transitions CPU hardware automatically reads these on privilege change Must be updated on every context switch
ESP+0x00: User EIP ESP+0x04: User CS (0x1B) ESP+0x08: User EFLAGS ESP+0x0C: User ESP ESP+0x10: User SS (0x23)
